INSERT INTO beacon_blocks (
            block_hash,
            block_root,
            deposit_sum,
            deposit_sum_aggregated,
            withdrawal_sum,
            withdrawal_sum_aggregated,
            pending_deposits_sum_gwei,
            parent_root,
            state_root
        )
        VALUES (
            $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9
        )
